      {
        "position": 1,
        "title": "Good quality and well made dog calming shirt",
        "text": "This is a really nice quality dog calming shirt with hood. It has a little bit of stretch to it. You can tighten it around the dog to help add comfort/a calming effect for the doggo.The color is a nice black. The material seems nice and is a dense and good quality and it is stitched and made very well. The Velcro is sewn on well and is a durable quality. The hood has a cinching mechanism to tighten on the dogs head if anyone wants to cover their dogs ears from rain or the elements. It won’t do much to dampen noises.The size chart is accurate. This fits my 80lb German Shepherd dog and my 90lb Labrador. It has a bit of give and is adjustable to be able to fit a small range of dogs within the size chart. Obviously a GSD and a lab are two different shapes as the GSD is tall and slim and the lab is tall and has a wide rib cage.For now it seems to be great quality and that it will last a long time with regular use and regular washing. However, I will update this review if things change. I don’t expect them to.I would definitely recommend this to anyone looking for a shirt with a hood for their dog. As far as the calming qualities I can’t comment definitively if it makes much of a difference, but I’ve bought and tried another very costly brand on my very high strung and high anxiety GSD and that brand didn’t help, so it could be based off the dog, breed, and the cause of your dog’s anxiety. This is calming shirt is worth the price it is listed at and having a hood is a fun thing. It arrived a day early and pretty quickly as well. So if you need one in a hurry it could just be the dog shirt for you.",
        "rating": 5,
        "date": "January 5, 2026",
        "author": "JRay",
        "author_link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEVM3X53JTYRYA4GCV6SAWQXHQHQ",
        "author_image": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/7ea4cc16-6a37-4f35-8905-5f432661dd4c._CR0%2C0%2C375%2C375_UX460_.jpg",
