      {
        "position": 2,
        "title": "Effective Anxiety Relief Vest That Truly Helped My Dog",
        "text": "I got the medium size for my twenty pound Scottish Terrier and it fit him perfectly. I really like the material of this vest. It is thick and feels well made. The Velcro is very good quality, not the usual kind you see. It sticks really well. The first time I put it on him, I went to adjust it and realized I actually had to use a little bit of force to pull it apart because the Velcro holds so firmly. Once I adjusted it a bit tighter, it seemed to work even better.My dog was a little confused at first. He is very fluffy, so when I put the vest on him it looked tight, but it was not uncomfortable for him at all.I tried it on him for the first time when there was a storm happening, and that is when I really noticed a difference. He is very scared of storms and normally he shakes nonstop and cannot even lay down to calm himself. Talking to him or massaging him does not help. With this vest on, he was able to lay down in his bed. He still shook a little at times, but it was different. It was like his body wanted to shake, then it would calm down once he felt the pressure of the vest.For me and my dog, this was definitely a win. If you have an anxious dog, this is something worth trying because it truly helped my dog.",
