        "title": "Quality and Comfort",
        "text": "My dog weighs 14 lbs with an 11 inch neck and 18 inch chest. The size Small fit her perfectly. The material is thick and durable making for a quality product! I like that it’s adjustable with the Velcro around the middle.The only thing my dog didn’t like was the hood. I think it’s because of the adjustable strap at the front. That’s the only thing that could be improved. Otherwise, it looks cute as a hoodie and she loves sleeping in it!Overall, I think it will be great when there is a need for calm due to fireworks or thunder.",
