        "title": "It put little Mickey to sleep during a thunderstorm",
        "text": "I ordered this vest for my Dash who gets anxious during thunder, and it’s been great. The adjustable fit hugs him snugly without restricting movement, and he seems much calmer during fireworks, storms, and when I leave the house.The fabric is medium weight and stretchy, so he’s comfortable all day. I like that the hood can cover his neck and head for extra calming.It’s easy to put on and take off, and the size fits my fur baby perfectly (I checked the size chart first). Definitely recommend for small dogs who get anxious.",
